      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "、Introduction 介绍自喜欢的物",
        "bbox": [
          0.1199400299850075,
          0.6284501061571125,
          0.4427786106946527,
          0.6454352441613588
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1.英语中通常使“Ilikeeating...”句型来介绍喜欢的物。注意区分食物的单复数。 回答用“Ilikeeating食物名词”来表达，注意物名词如果是可数名词，必须用复数。",
        "bbox": [
          0.08195902048975512,
          0.6503892427459307,
          0.9045477261369316,
          0.6886058032554848
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.描述食物味道的形容词有“delicious,tasty，yummy,yukky”等，同学们要注意积累哦。",
        "bbox": [
          0.11294352823588207,
          0.692144373673036,
          0.8575712143928036,
          0.7098372257607927
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_20",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "二、Asking询问他人喜欢的食物",
        "bbox": [
          0.12193903048475763,
          0.7140835102618542,
          0.39780109945027486,
          0.7310686482661005
        ],
        "order": 21
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_21",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "what表示“什么”，问对方喜欢吃/喝什么，我们可以问： What do you like eating?=What do you like to eat? 你喜欢吃什么? What do you like drinking?=What do you like to drink? 你喜欢喝什么? What'syour favouritefood?你最喜欢的食物是什么？",
        "bbox": [
          0.12093953023488256,
          0.7338995046001415,
          0.7536231884057971,
          0.8152866242038217
        ],
        "order": 22
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_color_textbook_教材全解1+1二年级下册英语上海牛津版_page_045_23",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（在森林里，熊猫先生开的食品店里来了两位客人。） Mr Panda: Hello, who are you? Little Rabbit :I'm Little Rabbit. I'm small and white. My ears are long. My eyes are red. Mr Panda: What do you like eating?",
        "bbox": [
